Requirements are summarized from **`Website UI Development.pdf`** (painting & plumbing scope, page list, global features, footer columns, UAE positioning). The **Ridge-style reference image** in the project assets illustrates the **calm, spacious, accent-driven** layout we want—not a literal copy of another brand’s name or logo.
